\c 22
\s Umfanekiso wedili lomtshado
\p
\v 1 UJesu wasephendula wabuya wakhuluma labo ngemifanekiso\x + 11.25; 17.4. Hlu. 18.14.\x*, wathi:
\v 2 Umbuso wamazulu ufananiswa lomuntu \add oy\add*inkosi\x + Luka 14.16-24.\x*, owenzela indodana yakhe idili lomtshado\x + 25.10. Isam. 19.7,9. Luka 12.36; 14.8. Joha. 2.2. Gen. 29.22.\x*;
\v 3 wasethuma inceku zakhe ukuthi zibize abanxusiweyo emtshadweni, kodwa kabavumanga ukubuya\x + Esta 6.14. Zaga 9.3,5. Zef. 1.7.\x*.
\v 4 Wabuya wathuma ezinye inceku\x + 21.36.\x*, esithi: Batsheleni abanxusiweyo \add ukuthi\add*: Khangelani, sengilungisile ukudla kwami kwemini\x + Luka 11.38; 14.12. Luka 11.37. Joha. 21.12,15.\x*, inkabi zami\x + Zaga 9.2.\x* lokunonileyo sekuhlatshiwe\x + Luka 15.23,27,30.\x*, izinto zonke sezilungile; wozani emtshadweni.
\v 5 Kodwa kabananzanga, bazihambela, omunye ensimini yakhe, omunye ekuthengiselaneni kwakhe;
\v 6 abaseleyo basebezibamba inceku zakhe ba\add zi\add*phatha kubi ba\add zi\add*bulala\x + 21.35.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa kwathi inkosi ikuzwa \add lokho\add* yathukuthela, yathuma amabutho ayo yabhubhisa labobabulali, yatshisa umuzi wabo\x + Luka 23.11.Dan. 9.26. Luka 19.27.\x*.
\v 8 Yasisithi encekwini zayo: Umtshado usulungile, kodwa abanxusiweyo bebengafanelanga\x + 10.11,13. Seb. 13.46. Isam. 3.4.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho yanini emahlanganweni ezindlela, njalo bonke elingabathola, libabizele emtshadweni.
\v 10 Lezonceku zaseziphuma zaya ezindleleni zabutha bonke ezabatholayo, ababi kanye labalungileyo; indlu yomtshado yasigcwala ngabahleziyo\x + 13.38,47; 25.2.\x*.
\v 11 Kwathi inkosi ingena ukukhangela ababehlezi ekudleni yabona khona umuntu owayengembathanga\x + Zef. 1.8. Isa. 61.10; 64.6. Isam. 3.4; 16.15; 19.8.\x* isembatho somtshado\x + 2 Kho. 10.22.\x*;
\v 12 yasisithi kuye: Mngane, ungene njani lapha ungelasembatho somtshado\x + 20.13.\x*? Kodwa yena waqunywa umlomo\x + 22.34. Mark. 1.25; 4.39 Luka 4.35. 1 Pet. 2.15.\x*.
\v 13 Inkosi yasisithi ezincekwini\x + 20.26.22.3,4,6,8,10. 13.41,49.\x*: Mbopheni inyawo lezandla, limsuse limphosele emnyameni ongaphandle; lapho kuzakuba khona ukukhala lokugedla amazinyo\x + 8.12.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba banengi ababiziweyo, kodwa balutshwana abakhethiweyo\x + 20.16.\x*.
\s Umthelo kaKesari
\p
\v 15 Khona-ke abaFarisi basuka, bacebisana ngokuthi bangamthiya njani ekukhulumeni\x + Mark. 12.13-37. Luka 20.20-38.\x*.
\v 16 Basebethuma kuye abafundi babo kanye labakaHerodi\x + Mark. 3.6; 12.13.Mark. 8.15.\x*, besithi: Mfundisi, siyazi ukuthi wena uqotho, ufundisa indlela kaNkulunkulu ngeqiniso, kawukhathaleli muntu, ngoba kawunanzi isimo sabantu\x + Zaga 24.23.\x*.
\v 17 Ngakho sitshele, wena ucabangani? Kuvunyelwe yini ukuthela\x + 17.25.\x* kuKesari, kumbe hatshi\x + Luka 3.1.\x*?
\v 18 Kodwa uJesu ebazi ububi babo wathi\x + 9.4.\x*: Bazenzisi, lingilingelani\x + Mark. 12.15.\x*?
\v 19 Ngitshengisani imali yokuthela. Basebeletha kuye \w udenariyo\w**.
\v 20 Wasesithi kubo: Ngokabani lumfanekiso lalumbhalo?
\v 21 Bathi: NgokaKesari. Wasesithi kubo: Ngakho mnikeni uKesari izinto zikaKesari; loNkulunkulu izinto zikaNkulunkulu\x + Roma 13.7.\x*.
\v 22 Kwathi sebezwile bamangala; bamtshiya bahamba\x + Mark. 12.12.\x*.
\s Ukuvuka kwabafileyo
\p
\v 23 Ngalolosuku kweza kuye abaSadusi\x + 3.7; 16.1,6,11,12.22.34. Seb. 4.1; 5.17; 23.6-8.\x*, abathi kakukho ukuvuka \add kwabafileyo\x + Seb. 23.8. Seb. 4.2.\x*\add*, basebembuza,
\v 24 besithi: Mfundisi, uMozisi wathi: Uba umuntu esifa engelabantwana, umfowabo uzamthatha umkakhe, amvusele umfowabo inzalo\x + Dute. 25.5.\x*.
\v 25 Kwakukhona phakathi kwethu izelamani eziyisikhombisa; owokuqala wasethatha umfazi wafa; futhi engelanzalo, watshiya umkakhe kumfowabo.
\v 26 Kwaba njalo lowesibili, lowesithathu, kwaze kwaba kowesikhombisa.
\v 27 Kwathi emva kwabo bonke kwafa lomfazi.
\v 28 Ngakho ekuvukeni \add kwabafileyo\add*, uzakuba ngumkabani kwabayisikhombisa? Ngoba bonke babelaye.
\v 29 Kodwa uJesu waphendula wathi kubo: Liduhile, lingayazi imibhalo\x + Joha. 20.9.\x*, loba amandla kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Kor. 6.14.\x*;
\v 30 ngoba ekuvukeni \add kwabafileyo\add* kabathathani, kabendiswa\x + 24.38. Luka 17.27.\x*, kodwa banjengengilosi zikaNkulunkulu ezulwini.
\v 31 Kodwa mayelana lokuvuka kwabafileyo\x + 1 Kor. 15.42,44,49,52. 1 Joha. 3.2.\x*, kalifundanga yini okwakhulunywa kini nguNkulunkulu, esithi:
\v 32 Mina nginguNkulunkulu kaAbrahama, loNkulunkulu kaIsaka, loNkulunkulu kaJakobe\x + Eks. 3.6. Seb. 7.32.\x*? UNkulunkulu kayisuye uNkulunkulu wabafileyo, kodwa owabaphilayo.
\v 33 Kwathi amaxuku ekuzwa amangala kakhulu ngokufundisa kwakhe\x + 7.28.\x*.
\s Umlayo wokuqala
\p
\v 34 Kwathi abaFarisi, sebezwile ukuthi uJesu ubaqume umlomo\x + 22.12.\x* abaSadusi\x + 22.23.\x*, babuthana ndawonye.
\v 35 Lomunye wabo, isazumthetho, wa\add m\add*buza\x + Luka 7.30; 10.25; 11.45,46,52; 14.3. Tit. 3.13. Luka 5.17. Mark. 12.28. Luka 20.39.\x*, emlinga, esithi\x + Luka 7.30; 10.25; 11.45,46,52; 14.3. Tit. 3.13. Luka 5.17.Mark. 12.28. Luka 20.39.\x*:
\v 36 Mfundisi, yiwuphi umlayo omkhulu emthethweni?
\v 37 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Wothanda iNkosi uNkulunkulu wakho, ngenhliziyo yakho yonke, langomphefumulo wakho wonke, langengqondo yakho yonke\x + Dute. 6.5. Luka 10.27.\x*;
\v 38 yiwo lowo umlayo owokuqala lomkhulu.
\v 39 Lowesibili ufanana lawo \add uthi\add*: Wothanda umakhelwane wakho njengalokhu uzi\add thanda wena\x + Levi 19.18. Mat. 19.19. Luka 10.27.\x*\add*.
\v 40 Kuleyomilayo emibili kweyeme umthetho wonke labaprofethi\x + 7.12. 1 Tim. 1.5.\x*.
\s UKristu losendo lwakhe
\p
\v 41 Kwathi sebebuthene abaFarisi, uJesu wababuza,
\v 42 esithi: Licabangani ngoKristu? Uyindodana kabani\x + Luka 20.41-44.\x*? Bathi kuye: NgekaDavida\x + 1.1.\x*.
\v 43 Wathi kubo: Pho uDavida wambiza njani ekuMoya \add ngokuthi\add* yiNkosi\x + 2 Sam. 23.2.\x*, esithi:
\v 44 INkosi yathi eNkosini yami: Hlala ngakwesokunene sami, ngize ngenze izitha zakho zibe yisenabelo senyawo zakho\x + Hlab. 110.1. Seb. 2.34,35. Heb. 1.13.\x*?
\v 45 Ngakho uba uDavida embiza ngokuthi yiNkosi, uyiNdodana yakhe njani?
\v 46 Njalo kwakungekho owayengamphendula ilizwi\x + Luka 14.6.\x*; kusukela ngalolosuku kakwabe kusaba khona umuntu olesibindi sokumbuza\x + Mark. 12.34. Luka 20.40.\x*.